title: Faith Hill - The Hits (MP3) {CTShoN} [CTRC]
description:
The Hits Album by: Faith Hill
The Hits is the first greatest hits album from country singer Faith
Hill issued in the United States. Originally slated for release on May
8, 2007, the album was delayed several times until it was finally
released on October 2, 2007.
Release Date: October 2, 2007

Duration: 59:10
